   http://lists.otrs.org/pipermail/otrs/2002-August/000147.html (martin)
- send bulk answer -
   http://lists.otrs.org/pipermail/otrs/2002-June/000066.html (martin)
- delete option for records (martin)
- improve ticket search with between x and y
